  "text": "Synuclein triple KO mice, synaptobrevin-2 KO mice, and WT mice maintained on C57BL/6 background were maintained and bred as described previously [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . Mice of either sex were used for stereotactic injections or primary neuronal culture. The animal protocols used in this study, as well as the overall mouse husbandry practices, were approved by the respective institutional animal care and use committees at University of Texas Southwestern Medical Center and Stanford University.",
